  <steps>
    <step order="1">Verify all 5 PRs (PR 1–5) merged to master. Run `gh pr list --state merged --base master --head 'work/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4*'`. If any PR is unmerged, STOP and block until merged.</step>
    <step order="2">Run final `/code-review` across all R4-touched files (PR 1–5 surface). Address any critical issues with hotfix commits.</step>
    <step order="3">Run final `/adr-check` to verify compliance with ADRs 001, 010, 013, 021, 024, 027, 028, 029, 034, 037.</step>
    <step order="4">Verify spec.md §Success Criteria checklist — all 15 boxes can be ticked. Run a final UAT sweep in spaarkedev1: hallucination test (ACME-only data → TL;DR mentions only ACME), 4 preferences visibly affect rendering, three-dot menu shows 6 actions, link click → modal opens, 403 → toast.</step>
    <step order="5">Final BFF publish-size measurement: `dotnet publish -c Release src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ -o deploy/api-publish/` — record final compressed size + cumulative delta vs R3 baseline. Confirm ≤+1 MB per NFR-02 and within 60 MB ceiling per CLAUDE.md §10.</step>
    <step order="6">Final CVE scan: `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive` + `npm audit --production --workspace=@spaarke/daily-briefing-components`. Confirm no new HIGH per NFR-01.</step>
    <step order="7">Author `projects/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4/notes/lessons-learned.md`. Capture: JPS deployment-as-first-class-concern lesson (R4's core thesis); spec path discovery friction (NotificationService.cs path mismatch); `sprk_playbookconsumer` extension feasibility (whatever task 030 decided); R3 PR #451 parallel-development coordination experience; any other gotchas encountered during execution.</step>
    <step order="8">Update README.md: Status = Complete, Phase = Complete, Progress = 100%, Completed Date set, all Graduation Criteria checkboxes ticked, Changelog entry appended.</step>
    <step order="9">Update plan.md: Status = Complete; all milestones ✅.</step>
    <step order="10">Verify TASK-INDEX.md has all 46 tasks marked ✅. Update if any are still 🔲 or 🔄.</step>
    <step order="11">Run `/repo-cleanup projects/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4` — review cleanup report, approve removal of notes/debug/, notes/spikes/, notes/drafts/. Archive notes/handoffs/ if any.</step>
    <step order="12">Run `/devops-project-sync` to refresh portfolio Issue with final state (Task Count, Status=Complete).</step>
    <step order="13">Optionally run `/devops-project-archive` to formally close the portfolio Issue with completion summary.</step>
    <step order="14">Final commit + push of wrap-up artifacts (lessons-learned, updated README/plan/TASK-INDEX). Tag the commit `daily-briefing-r4-complete`.</step>
  </steps>

